 in fact if they do or don't sell these pre-leveled charactors. If they do sell these charactors I have some questions I hope you folks will be kind enough to answer for me. <br>  <br> 1) Are these charactors denoted or marked in any manner in game ? <br>  <br> 2) Are there any restrictions placed on what servers these charactors are introduced to ? <br>  <br> 3) Are there any special restrictions other than the above ? <br>  <br> 4) Is there any consensus of what type of MMORPG player is likely to buy one of these charactors ? <br>  <br> 5) How do EQ players in general feel about this ? (please do not answer this question if this topic angers you. I am just interested in reasonable and rational opinions) <br>  <br> 6) If you bought one of these charactors do you feel you got good value for your money ? <br>  <br> 7) If you bought one of these charactors how did or do you feel about it now overall ? <br>  <br>  <br> NOTE: the reason I am asking these questions has to do with MMORPG'ing and not EQ itself. I myself have never had a interest other than playing a game and building my own charactors. I have never bought any charactors or accounts for any game and I don't see myself ever going contrary to my history. <br>  <br> Thanks in advance for your answers and opinions and forgive me if I am grossly ignorant of how EQ works because I am <img src="http://media.ign.com/boardfaces/1.gif" border="0" alt="happy" hspace="0" vspace="0">  <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">The only knowledge I possess is the fact of my ignorance -Socrates <br> Support US troops <br>  <br> </div></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23lockedtopic">Locked Topic</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=46684679" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?us