ting you in the back.&quot; <br>  <br> After getting booted and ignored he petitioned a gm to whine about how he was treated. The gm being as polite as he could basically told him to move on and try to listen to your group when they explain something in the future when this guy asks the gm, &quot;just how do I kick and taunt anyway?&quot; The gm/guide hearing this proceeded to walk the guy through the answer then realizing he was talking to a 50+ character basically got the guy to tell him flat out, yes he had bought this account, so what? Nothing, the gm would just like to contact this seller to get him to help you out, could he have the email of that person please? From that email the gm uncovered an account and doing some research discovered that this same credit card number had set up over 25 accounts in the past 2 months and closed each new one with a brand new 50+ character them within a week like clockwork. This led him to the actual guy selling the accounts and the banning of all accounts and cdkeys that had been originally been set up by him within about a weeks time. <br>  <br> What's the funny part? One of the questions the gm asked was, &quot;I see your station name is 'Ebaccount021' any particular reason why you chose that name?&quot; <br>  <br> &quot;I dunno, just haven't bothered to change it yet, I wanted to try the game out first.&quot; <br> <p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23lockedtopic">Locked Topic</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=46797746" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=559276">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=559276">Post History</a></td></tr>
